{"id":"f6d37bc6-26ba-4abf-8f71-cbdcdf274ab8","name":"Dragon Ball Super S.H. Figuarts Action Figure Android 17 (Universe Survival Saga) 14cm","slug":"dragon-ball-super-s.h.-figuarts-action-f","description":"<p><b>Dragon Ball Super </b>action figure of <b>Android 17 </b>in <strong>S.H. Figuarts </strong>collection,size approx.14 cm. <b>Official product</b> by <strong>Tamashii Nations</strong>.</p>\n<p>From the Universe Survival Saga of \"Dragon Ball Super,\" the mighty Android 17 joins S.H.Figuarts! Standing 135mm tall and made of ABS and PVC plastic, you can display it in dynamic poses with the many included options and effect parts!</p>\n<p><strong>Android 17</strong> is the 17th artificial human created by<strong> Doctor Gero</strong> to take revenge on <strong>Son Goku</strong>.</p>\n<p>Twin brother of <strong>Android 18</strong>, he is one of the major antagonists of the Artificial Humans Saga before being absorbed by <strong>Cell</strong>. On the latter's death, N ° 17 is resuscitated thanks to the <strong>Dragon Balls</strong> and becomes an animal protector. Recruited years later by <strong>Son Gokû</strong> to participate in the Tournament of Power, he was the winner of the <strong>Super Dragon Balls</strong> and restored the 7 universes destroyed by <strong>Zen'Ô</strong>.</p>\n<p>Complete the duo with <a href=\"https://www.lacitedesnuages.be/en/22369-dragon-ball-super-sh-figuarts-action-figure-android-18-universe-survival-saga-14cm.html\">Android 18</a> !</p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\">Contents:</span></strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Main Body</li>\n<li>Four pairs of optional hands</li>\n<li>Three optional expression parts</li>\n<li>Optional hair part</li>\n<li>Energy bomb effect</li>\n<li>Attack effect</li>\n</ul>\n<p>This product is not a toy or product for children. It is a collectors item intended for adults only.</p>","metaTitle":null,"metaDescription":null,"model":null,"releaseDate":null,"image":null,"condition":null,"edition":null